[
  {
    "text": "Hello, everyone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "I am Zhehong from Game Center Engineering team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'm really excited to walk you through ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "how SharePlay has been integrated with Game Center. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "Game Center is Apple's social gaming platform. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "Players can add friends, compete on leaderboards, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "earn achievements, and see everything in one place ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "with Player Activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "Game Center also supports ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "great multiplayer experiences for players, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "including invitation, matchmaking, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "real-time gameplay, and voice chat. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "This year, we're excited to bring SharePlay support ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "to Game Center. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "Players can already invite friends, contacts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=39"
  },
  {
    "text": "and nearby players to play together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "SharePlay enables them to share gaming experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "right in the moment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, if your players are on a FaceTime call ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "or a Messages group, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can immediately jump into a game together. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "Imagine your players are in a Messages group ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "with some friends, and they want to play a game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "They can simply start an audio call from the group chat. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "Their friends will receive the invitation as a FaceTime call. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then it's time to launch your game.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take NBA 2K23 Arcade Edition as an example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can click Play Now in the title screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "and select Multiplayer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then tap the Play With Friends button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "After that, clicking Online NBA button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "will bring you the game Settings page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's set it to four quarters ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "and two minutes for each quarter. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click on Next. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "This brings up the Game Center multiplayer UI, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "where players will see the brand-new mode selection screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "that includes the SharePlay option. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tapping the Start SharePlay button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "will activate a group activity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "Players can join and play together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "by simply tapping the Open button on their end. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you already use Game Center ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "to support multiplayer in your game, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will get full SharePlay integration ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "with just one small update. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I will show you how to enable SharePlay for your game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "Currently, if you present the GKMatchmakerViewController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "players will see the mode selection screen by default. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you want to adopt SharePlay integration, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "the first step is to add the entitlement of Group Activities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can do that by going to the project settings, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "and in the Signing & Capabilities tab, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "just search for Group Activities and select it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "With GroupActivities capability enabled, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "the mode selection screen will show the SharePlay option. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are using Game Center Multiplayer UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "provided by GKMatchmakerViewController, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "that is the only step you have to do. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "You are done! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "On the other hand, if you are building ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "your own multiplayer UI using Game Center APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "you could choose to integrate with SharePlay's APIs directly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "But since you're using Game Center APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "we've also got you covered. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's still really easy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "You already added GroupActivities capability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Xcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you want to call some GameKit APIs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can call the API to start a Group Activity on SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, add the players to the recipient list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, call the API to start a match. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's jump into the code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, call GKMatchmaker .shared.startGroupActivity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that GameKit can notify your game when a player ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the FaceTime call wants to join a match. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, add the player to the recipient list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, call GKMatchmaker.shared.findMatch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "to start a match. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "With just these steps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "your game is now supporting SharePlay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "As simple as that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "To wrap up, Game Center's integration with SharePlay ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "makes it easier for players to start games with friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're using Game Center UI to build ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "a multiplayer experience, you just need to add ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=247"
  },
  {
    "text": "a GroupActivities capability in Xcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are building your own custom UI, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "use the new APIs provided in GKMatchmaker. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're new to using Game Center to build ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "multiplayer experiences, I suggest you watch this video: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Tap into Game Center: Leaderboards, Achievements, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Multiplayer\" from WWDC 2020. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for watching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110338/?time=273"
  }
]